You're right. I am good at pissing people off. Over the years playing EQ, I would say I've cooled down ALOT. Anyone remember Trist vs Tamas, the epic flame battle? A couple months ago, we reconciled and he even came on a few raids with us and I found out I really sincerely liked him. Ah well.<br>
<br>
But what really pisses me off and gets me going is when my family or friends are wronged. I don't give a flaming rats SHIT who you are, if you've hurt my family I'm going to revile you. I'm going to piss you off. I'm probably going to piss you off alot. Why? Because it gets your attention on me and not the family. I have a thick skin, and I'll take your beatings all day long. I really don't give a shit.<br>
<br>
Those that ~really~ know me well are the only ones that count. Dipshits like Stehe and Ulwern can flame me all they want and I won't care. You flame my guild, my compadres, my out and out family and you will incur my wrath. I have enough vitriol left to make you hate me just a little bit more. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><a href="http://www.theradiant.net"><img border="0" src="http://www.theradiant.net/TristSig7.jpg" width="310" height="335"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/ucyllyan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cyllyan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Duracyl the mana battery</span><br>  Posts: 132<br> <font color=#00CCFF>(9/23/02 5:05:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=534.topic&index=116>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good ole Radiant? eh?</span><hr size=1> Die thread, die...<br>
